AUDIO: 'and we\'ve broken them up into domains. So, for me, I have memory, productivity, research, content, community, on and on and on. What you would have specifically would be different depending on what you do. But, the idea is we do a lot of different things, and they have specific'

[02:07] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'domains. For example, let\'s take a look at the research domain. I do a lot of research, and under each domain are a number of discrete or individual tasks. For me, I\'m often looking stuff up on YouTube. I need to do deep research into'

