VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'things. I need to deal with light rag. I want to have a morning report. I want to watch my competitors. On and on and on and on. So, every domain\'s going to have individual tasks. Each of these tasks, if this is something we do regularly, A,'

[02:31] [scene:talk]
