VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'business life. Have you codified it in this manner? Have you turned every task into a skill? Do you have a way of tracking all of this and optimizing it? Chances are no. And if that\'s the case, even if you do nothing else with this whole ClaudeOS system, doing the memory,'

